OL,5, Domestic energy prices could be capped 
OL,6, based on the time of day that          
OL,7, households use their appliances, the   
OL,8, regulator Ofgem has said.              
OL,10,FThe watchdog said it has launched early
OL,11,Fdiscussions about a "dynamic" price cap
OL,12,Fthat changes as consumers became more  
OL,13,Fflexible.                              
OL,15,FIt said it would become harder to      
OL,16,Fretain a universal price cap that is   
OL,17,Fsuitable for everyone.                 
OL,19,FSo it is considering a range of options
OL,20,Ffor changing the current system.       
